                    <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Swica:</strong> Popular with both locals and international residents</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                    <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Helsana:</strong> Known for multilingual support</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                    <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>CSS:</strong> Large nationwide provider with good coverage</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                    <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Sanitas:</strong> Active in Ticino with good services</span>
